     1Ôćĺ# Configuration
     3ÔćĺThis section details the configuration options available in the ***book.toml***:
     4Ôćĺ- **[General]** configuration including the `book`, `rust`, `build` sections
     5Ôćĺ- **[Preprocessor]** configuration for default and custom book preprocessors
     6Ôćĺ- **[Renderer]** configuration for the HTML, Markdown and custom renderers
     7Ôćĺ- **[Environment Variable]** configuration for overriding configuration options in your environment
     8Ôćĺ
